### Auth Service - Production Environment
### Base URL: https://prod-api-id.execute-api.region.amazonaws.com/prod/auth

### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = https://prod-api-id.execute-api.region.amazonaws.com/prod/auth
@contentType = application/json

### Test Data for Production
@testEmail = prod-test@example.com
@testPassword = ProdSecurePassword123!
@testName = Production Test User

### Production Environment Health Check
